To update Dear ImGui files go to https://github.com/ocornut/imgui/tree/docking.
1) Switch to a commit with the tag X.XX.X-docking.
2) Copy all .h & .cpp files in the main imgui directory as well as the dx9 & win32 backends EXCEPT for the imconfig.h file.

3) Copy files from https://github.com/ocornut/imgui/tree/master/misc/cpp

4) Download source from https://github.com/aiekick/ImGuiFileDialog/releases and put in imgui/ImGuiFileDialog.

If updating ImGui, make sure to copy the settings from imconfig.h & ImGuiFileDialogConfig.h.

- uncrafted
